summaries.full: Bill's attempt to stage a 'safety net' meeting for polygamist leaders is hindered by Alby and Home Plus objectors. Barb makes an effort to find common ground with her mother; Nicki learns the extent of Adaleen's isolation; Marge despairs over the quandary involving Ana and Goran; Cara Lynn impresses her math teacher, and Greg.

summaries.short: The Henricksons try to put on a unified face during Christmas, but the family is tested by numbing revelations from Barb, Marge & Adaleen.
summaries.full: The Henricksons try to put on a unified face during Christmas, but the family is tested amidst numbing revelations. Meanwhile, Lura takes drastic measures in response to Alby's zealous efforts to 'purify' the compound; Lois drifts towards the deep end; Bill tries to soften up a senator; Ben bonds with Heather; and Cara Lynn looks for answers about her father.

summaries.short: Season Five Premiere. In the aftermath of his election, Bill faces an uphill battle to win over his constituents and employees.
summaries.full: Season Five Premiere. After some restful post-election days in the wilderness, reality hits the Henricksons hard on their return to Salt Lake City. At Home Plus, Bill tries to bolster morale in the wake of his polygamist revelation. On Capitol Hill, he faces an uphill battle for his political life. And at home, Bill must assuage some very real concerns of his wives and kids.

summaries.full: With his swearing-in ceremony only days away, Bill searches for ways to overcome the anti-polygamist sentiment swelling among State officials. Meanwhile, Barb, Nicki and Margene struggle with personal revelations; Nicki pushes for Cara Lynn's adoption; Lois learns the source of her ailment; and Ben rewards Heather for her sensitivity.

summaries.short: In the Season Four finale, Bill faces last-minute threats to his candidacy; the three wives feel the strain as Election Day arrives.
summaries.full: (Season Four finale). With the election only days away, Bill puts the squeeze on Paley to protect his candidacy. But Marilyn has an ace up her sleeve that threatens to wreck Bill's chances. Meanwhile, Nicki gets news that seems too good to be true; and a late-breaking polygamist scandal forces Bill and his three wives to rethink their bold post-election plans.
